```

#### Touch (tap)

Requires `hasTouch` browser context. Use for mobile-emulated interactions:

```
playwright_execute { code: "await page.tap('.mobile-menu-btn')" }
playwright_execute { code: "await page.touchscreen.tap(200, 300)" }
```

#### Dispatch synthetic events

For custom events or events not covered by built-in actions:

```
playwright_execute { code: "await page.locator('#btn').dispatchEvent('click')" }
playwright_execute { code: "const dt = await page.evaluateHandle(() => new DataTransfer()); await page.locator('#src').dispatchEvent('dragstart', { dataTransfer: dt })" }
```

