#### File downloads

The relay maps `Browser.setDownloadBehavior` to per-page `Page.setDownloadBehavior` and synthesizes `Browser.download*` events, so Playwright downloads work in extension mode:

```
playwright_execute { code: "const [download] = await Promise.all([page.waitForEvent('download'), page.click('#download-btn')]); const path = await download.path(); return path;" }
```

#### Persistent state across calls

```
playwright_execute { code: "state.formData = { name: 'Test', email: 'a@b.com' };" }
playwright_execute { code: "await page.fill('#name', state.formData.name);" }
```

